data.title: Sigh: Disbarred Birther Montgomery Blair Sibley Petitions Supreme Court on Obama's Birth Certificate
data.meta_description: Montgomery Blair Sibley, a disbarred attorney waging a write-in campaign for president on the platform that Barack Obama isn't a natural-born U.S. citizen, is now claiming he will force the issue before the Supreme Court.
